How To Increase Number Of Replicas
first check deployment
$ kubectl get deployment

Check pods
$ kubectl get pods

Increase Number of replicas 
$ kubectl scale deployment/<deployment_name> --replicas=<number_of_replicas>

again check number of pods
$ kubectl get pods 

Decrease Number of replicas
$ kubectl scale deployment/<deployment_name> --replicas=<number_of_replicas>

again check number of pods
$ kubectl get pods 

Check Number of replicas  controller 
$ kubectl get rc
